{"tid":2065012,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"表特版正妹鄭乃馨撞臉TWICE娜璉　網起底是理科「工地西施」","createTime":"2020-06-15T08:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T15:42:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"25c46453f2be29f7269b99c5dc79f99e80bb3ac2","tid":2065012,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"來自泰國的鄭乃馨（Nene）上WeTV《創造營2020》，外表清新、皮膚白皙的她，過去曾是PTT表特版人氣正妹。她在節目第二階段，鄭乃馨人氣排名更爬升到第二，她有感而發說：「從16歲到現在已經6年了，我做了很多工作，我特別特別熱愛舞台。」<br />\n<br />\n鄭乃馨在節目中被黃子韜誇讚歌唱實力如CD，讓他有心動感覺。4年前鄭乃馨被PTT網友PO照分享，有眼尖網友發現她是泰國人，還找出她自彈自唱影片，直呼她讓人有戀愛感。<br />\n<br />\n而外表甜美的鄭乃馨被起底是讀理科學土木工程，節目曝光她學習搬磚塊照，網友形容是「工地西施」，也有網友說她外表神似TWICE成員娜璉，因而備受矚目。<br />\n <br />\n21歲的鄭乃馨在2015年以泰國女團MilkShake成員出道，期間推出兩首單曲《SHARE》、《JOH》，在Youtube分別狂收600萬及500萬的點擊量。鄭乃馨曾擔任《Talk Talk》電台DJ，近期更在泰國爆紅BL劇《只為我們天生一對》演出音樂社秘書。"},{"pid":"431cfd2bf6fc823448d19abf7b11125c687cdd41","tid":2065012,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4940/d4940711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4940%2Fd4940711.jpg&h=67749abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 鄭乃馨（Nene）參與選秀節目。（圖／WeTV提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4940/d4940712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4940%2Fd4940712.jpg&h=e9fb9d5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ff71e14d10fa25fd8366598c83560602c1240f1","tid":2065012,"uid":555,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:34:50.000Z","msg":"屌奶星靚過娜璉好撚多啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db8eade6281c0b4540669a0041c85cc2bf9eab1","tid":2065012,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img s